snippet.title: The Amazing Spider-Man 2 video game launch trailer UK | HD
snippet.description:
The Amazing Spider-Man 2 video game launch trailer. Can you defeat Spider-Man's deadliest foes? On May 5th, Peter Parker returns in an all-new open world adventure!
Pre-order at GAME to get the Web Threads Suit Pack for PS3, PS4, Xbox 360, and PC - http://bit.ly/1m5DSha
